  72:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     The compilation define USE_HAL_USART_REGISTER_CALLBACKS when set to 1
  73:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
  74:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c **** 
  75:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     [..]
  76:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     Use Function HAL_USART_RegisterCallback() to register a user callback.
  77:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     Function HAL_USART_RegisterCallback() allows to register following callbacks:
  78:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) TxHalfCpltCallback        : Tx Half Complete Callback.
  79:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) TxCpltCallback            : Tx Complete Callback.
  80:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) RxHalfCpltCallback        : Rx Half Complete Callback.
  81:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) RxCpltCallback            : Rx Complete Callback.
  82:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) TxRxCpltCallback          : Tx Rx Complete Callback.
  83:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) ErrorCallback             : Error Callback.
  84:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) AbortCpltCallback         : Abort Complete Callback.
  85:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) RxFifoFullCallback        : Rx Fifo Full Callback.
  86:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) TxFifoEmptyCallback       : Tx Fifo Empty Callback.
  87:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) MspInitCallback           : USART MspInit.
ARM GAS  /tmp/cc8mN3FX.s 			page 3


  88:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     (+) MspDeInitCallback         : USART MspDeInit.
  89:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****     This function takes as parameters the HAL peripheral handle, the Callback ID
