 245:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****              in the data register is transmitted but is changed by the parity bit.
 246:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART polarity
 247:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_usart.c ****         (++) USART phase
